      * processTags (this should invoke and execute the new TagProcessor

    * Undecided
      * readFeed
      * downloadStream
      * child
      * db
      * dbUpdateFeed
      * dbUpdateStream

    * main
      * banner
      * syntax

  * NEW:

    * TagProcessor
      * assoc
      * output
